Windows package support validation log
Date: 2026-07-14
Scope: dotfiles/Brewfile compared with dotfiles/Wingetfile

Summary
- Brewfile entries audited: 51 (41 brew + 10 cask)
- Wingetfile entries present: 8
- Result: core tools are covered, but many Brewfile packages are not yet mapped in Wingetfile.

Already covered in Wingetfile
- Git.Git (brew: gh ecosystem prerequisite via Git)
- GitHub.cli (brew: gh)
- Microsoft.VisualStudioCode (cask: visual-studio-code)
- JanDeDobbeleer.OhMyPosh (brew: oh-my-posh)
- Neovim.Neovim (brew: neovim)
- Docker.DockerDesktop (container runtime)
- RancherDesktop.RancherDesktop (cask: rancher equivalent)
